# applied-ai-engineering

Public curriculum monorepo for **format**, **application**, and **deployment** patterns.

## Discipline

- No secrets, `.env`, PDFs, or lab paths (`mnt/ai_lab_os`, `05_llc`) in commits.
- One `.venv` per `projects/<module>/`.
- Prefer small PRs: one module or track at a time.
- README defers narrative to [obversarystudios.org](https://obversarystudios.org); eval research: [observatory](https://github.com/obversarystudios/observatory).

## Pre-push

```bash
rg -i "mnt/ai_lab_os|05_llc|obversary_personal|sk-[a-zA-Z0-9]{20,}" .
```

## Layout

- `INDEX.md` — lesson ↔ module map
- `projects/README.md` — build order, recipes A–L
- `python_cheatsheet.md` — M01–M15 deployment patterns
